data.text:
@NigelCulkin You’re Mix92.6 through and through!

#SACFC😇

👊 Some team

#SACFC 😇 https://t.co/yeMm52LvkG

❌ No Post Match Interview

😩 Unfortunately, due to a corrupt card, our post match interview from today has been lost. 

🤦‍♂️ We apologise to those fans keen to hear David's thoughts. 

#WeGoAgain
#BackStronger
#AdminOut 

#SACFC 😇 https://t.co/iq6AjY8zFf

The Saints Player of the Game goes to Devante Stanley. 

Saints 🟡 3 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇 https://t.co/x4ObdBA8oP

⏱️ FULL TIME

🤩 Jeffers Hat-trick
🙅‍♂️ Clean Sheet
🌲 Three Points

🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿 It's over to you now England...
🍻 Be sure to join us in The Clubhouse after the game!

#SACFC 😇 https://t.co/AmIYPD5Qvw

90+5' - GOAL!

Ejeheri parries away a close range Joe Neal effort, but only into the path of Jeffers who is able to turn the ball in to complete his hattrick. 

Saints 🟡 3 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇 https://t.co/Ak7Gbxzf7s

90+1' - A deflection in the Saints area falls fortunately for Jamie Yila, whose shot was saved by Berry who did well to react on short notice. 

Saints 🟡 2 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

88' - Today's attendance is 1018, thank you to both sets of fans for your support today. 

Saints 🟡 2 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

85' - 🔁 SAINTS SUBSTITUTION 

⏬ Munashe Sundire 
⏫ Huw Dawson 

Saints 🟡 2 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

84' - A long ball finds Esam in behind the Saints back-line.

He chests the ball down and looks to shoot first time, however he is unable to keep his effort down as the ball goes high into the stands. 

Saints 🟡 2 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

82' - 🟨 YELLOW CARD 

Berry receives a booking for a mistimed challenge on Yearn, as he attempts to clear away a dangerous through ball. 

Saints 🟡 2 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

80' - A headed clearance from the Saints falls kindly for Tom Blackwell.

He opts to shoot from close range, however Dylan Berry comes out quickly to make the save. 

Saints 🟡 2 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

78' - 🔁 SAINTS SUBSTITUTION 

⏬ Mitchell Weiss
⏫ Joe Neal 

Saints 🟡 2 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

78' - 🔁 CLARETS SUBSTITUTION 

⏬ Henry Ochieng
⏫ Samson Esam 

Saints 🟡 2 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

76' - 🟨 YELLOW CARD 

Stanley goes into the book after he was deemed to be time wasting.

Saints 🟡 2 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

73' - Jeffers pokes a through ball to Weiss on the edge of the box.

Weiss is able to swivel away from his marker creating room for a shot, however he drags his effort marginally wide of the far post. 

Saints 🟡 2 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

69' - GOAL!

Jeffers steps up to take a freekick on the edge of the Chelmsford area. He manages to squeeze his shot through the Clarets wall, taking it past Ejeheri into the far left corner. 

Saints 🟡 2 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇 https://t.co/5UM6e2Olfe

68' - 🟨 YELLOW CARD 

Tom Blackwell goes into the book for a foul on Sundire. 

Saints 🟡 1 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

64' - 🔁 CLARETS SUBSTITUTION 

⏬ Jazzi Barnum-Bobb
⏫ Simeon Jackson 

Saints 🟡 1 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

59' - A fast break for the Saints is worked towards Jeffers in the box. 

He looks to place his shot into the bottom corner, however Ejeheri is able to get down well to parry the ball away.

Saints 🟡 1 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

55' - The ball is worked to Shaun Jeffers in space at the back post, he shoots first time firing his effort into the side netting. 

Saints 🟡 1 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

53' - Substitute Lodovica plays a dangerous across the face of goal, however no Chelmsford player is there to meet it as the Saints come away with possession. 

Saints 🟡 1 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

51' - 🔁 CLARETS SUBSTITUTION 

⏬ Louis Dunne
⏫ Harry Lodovica

Saints 🟡 1 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

SECOND HALF: Chelmsford get the game restarted. 

Saints 🟡 1 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

⏱️ HALF TIME

🙋‍♂️ Saints lead through SJ9! 

#SACFC 😇 https://t.co/P5jhMZEIF7

40' - GOAL!

Jeffers slots his penalty straight down the middle to give the Saints the lead on the stroke of half time.

Saints 🟡 1 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇 https://t.co/SoyJy5ZDyA

39' - Penalty to the Saints 

Jeffers looks to get on the end of a Banton through ball, however he's brought down by Eduino Vaz earning a spot kick.  

Saints 🟡 0 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

28' - A Saints counter attack is worked to Mitchell Weiss on the edge of the box.

He elects to shoot from range, with his effort rolling comfortably towards Ejeheri as Chelmsford come away with possession. 

Saints 🟡 0 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

26' - A short corner is played to Devante Stanley on the right hand side. 

He plays a deep cross towards the far post, however no Saints player can reach it as the ball goes behind for a goal kick. 

Saints 🟡 0 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

18' - The best chance of the game so far falls to the Saints. 

Weiss is able to play Jeffers in behind but his effort goalward is tame, as goalkeeper Ejeheri can collect the ball with ease. 

Saints 🟡 0 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

9' - Chelmsford look to counter after Joy Mukena was dispossessed. 

They work their attack to Tom Blackwell on the left side, who plays a dangerous ball across goal however no Clarets players are there to meet it.  

Saints 🟡 0 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

6' - A long through ball for Chelmsford finds Tom Blackwell in behind the Saints defence. 

He runs through one on one but is unable to convert, firing a close range shot into the side netting. 

Saints 🟡 0 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

4' - A short corner is worked into Shaun Jeffers on the edge box, who fires goalward but is unable to keep his effort down as the ball goes high into the stands. 

Saints 🟡 0 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

3' - A floated cross from Banton looks to reach Stanley at the back-post, however Chelmsford are able to intercept and head the ball behind for a corner. 

Saints 🟡 0 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

KICKOFF: The home side get the game underway. 

Saints 🟡 0 - 0 ⚪ Clarets 

#SACFC 😇

📃 TEAM SHEET

Here is your Saints Starting XI to face @OfficialClarets in the @TheVanaramaNL South. 

#SACFC 😇 https://t.co/PEGQPhkSuB

data.text:
🗣️ David Noble discusses our early kick-off on the coast. 

▶️ Watch here:
👉 https://t.co/1Fi0tQNVd4

#SACFC 😇 https://t.co/Z2lIh2p4jC

The Saints Player of the Match has been awarded to Zane Banton. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇 https://t.co/UttHTPQ7hN

We'd like to thank the travelling Saints fans for making the trip down for today's game. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

⏱️ FULL TIME

🤝 The points are shared. 

#SACFC 😇 https://t.co/G0CQRz0o0K

90+1' - 🟨 YELLOW CARD

George Wilkinson goes into the referee's book. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

89' - The Saints continue to pressurise the Dover backline in search of a late winner. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

82' - The ball falls to Banton following a corner, whose powerful first time shot flies just wide of the far post. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

79' - The ball breaks kindly for Kandi in the Saints box following a deflection.

He looks to prod the ball home, however his effort sneaks marginally wide of the post. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

79' - 🔁 SAINTS SUBSTITUTION 

⏬ Huw Dawson
⏫ Chris Paul

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

77' - 🔁 SAINTS SUBSTITUTION 

⏬ Mitchell Weiss
⏫ Joe Neal

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

74' - Dover come forward following a spell of Saints pressure, as Judd sends a cross into the box.

Substitute Chike Kandi gets on the end of it and directs a header at Berry who reacts well to catch the ball at close range. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

72' - 🔁 WHITES SUBSTITUTION 

⏬ Alfie Pavey
⏫ Reece Grant

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

71' - Callum Adebiyi ventures forward down the left-hand-side, with his long-range effort flying past the post.

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

CORRECTION:

Luke Wanadio has been replaced, not Lee Martin. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

66' - Huw Dawson sends a long ball towards Jeffers at the back post, whose tame header at goal is easily caught by Nelson. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

64' - 🔁 WHITES SUBSTITUTION 

⏬ Lee Martin
⏫ Chike Kandi

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

63' - 🟨 YELLOW CARD

Kyran Wiltshire receives a yellow card for a handball just outside the area. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

56' - A corner for the Saints finds Joy Mukena, with his powerful headed effort cannoning off the crossbar. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

55' - The ball falls to Wiltshire on the edge of the box following a corner.

He elects to shoot from range, with keeper Nelson having to parry his effort over the bar. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

52' - Banton sends a cross towards the back post for Jeffers.

He gets his head to it but is unable to control his effort as the ball loops high over the crossbar. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

SECOND HALF: The Saints get the game restarted. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

⏱️ HALF TIME

⚽ Three pens in the 1st half, Dover convert, as does Jeffers first time of asking, but with the 2nd City spot kick saved, the scores are tied at the break. 

#SACFC 😇 https://t.co/ZYQ6jc7DF4

44' - Penalty Saved

Jeffers looks to put the ball to the same side as he did with the first penalty, however the keeper is wise to it diving the right way to prevent the Saints taking the lead. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

43' - Penalty for the Saints

St Albans win the ball back following the kick-off and come forward quickly, with a challenge on Tafari Moore in the box being deemed as a foul. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

42' - GOAL!

Jeffers is able to convert, sending the keeper the wrong way to calmly slot the ball home.

Whites ⚪ 1 - 1 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇 https://t.co/SNXCzIk9Ry

41' - 🟨 YELLOW CARD 

Banton is booked for an altercation following being fouled. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 0 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

40' - Penalty for the Saints

Zane Banton is taken down attempting to get on the end of a cross, giving St Albans the chance to equalise. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 0 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

31' - Huw Dawson fires a long-range effort goalward, almost finding the bottom left corner if not for a timely save from Stuart Nelson. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 0 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

27' - Goal for Dover

Luke Wanadio is able to convert the penalty, powering the ball past Dylan Berry into the bottom left corner. 

Whites ⚪ 1 - 0 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

26' - Penalty to Dover

A handball given against Kyran Wiltshire gives Dover the chance to take the lead.

Whites ⚪ 0 - 0 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

20' - A through ball from Dawson sends Jeffers through on goal. 

He rounds the keeper and looks to have scored, however the Dover defence do well to recover and clear the ball off the line. 

Whites ⚪ 0 - 0 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇

17' - Jeffers looks to finds Weiss with a dinked ball into the box, however Myles Judd is able to intercept and clear the ball behind for a corner. 

Whites ⚪ 0 - 0 🔵 Saints

#SACFC 😇
